Bakayoko to @lequipe: &quot;I experienced difficult moments at Milan, especially at the beginning. I'm sad to leave, but that's life. Gattuso? Complicated relationship, we didn't understand each other. I don't really want to talk about him.&quot; <br />
<br />
Bakayoko: &quot;If I took Italian lessons? At one point yes, then I stopped. I learned Italian with my teammates every day. And since things wasn't good at the beginning, I didn't take the time to learn. I woke up late (smiles).&quot;

